        "TileImage": "$($repository 0f88cdaa-d784-4951-8696-ea3065cc6228).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47 \r\rAn unusual contract for you days before Halloween. Retired pro-wrestler &quot;The Funeral Director&quot; years ago had his in-ring outfit stolen. He recently found out his lost gear is in the  posession of Leonard Parsons.  The client&apos;s request is to retrieve his ring attire and punish Parsons and his accomplices in the style of The Funeral Director&apos;s signature &quot;Buried while Breathing&quot; match which stipulates you deposit the targets in an open grave and bury them alive.\r\rGood hunting",
